Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,== OCR ==
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布烈絲  蓮娜  莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格拉迪亞…現在為何要襲擊這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情結束後才去想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次可能是最後一次在這裡換衫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來發生過很多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們真無禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對方是亞人  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  牠們很快便會打破水槽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  你們兩個快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉謝爾  拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要忍受那個程序
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要忍耐  若混入其他錯誤訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,inner metal…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便不會達到最佳效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又地震嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快支持不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰不懂游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絲莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們先上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇你也快走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…年紀大捱不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真嘔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.80,0:08:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是東京嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直好像另一個生態系統
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子無處可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道格拉迪亞的目標並不是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又地震
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出所料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來這裡碰巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在散播費挪現象的龍脈之上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種景色…真美麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直…就是想看見這種景色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣子逃去哪裡也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去到那裡或許有轉機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來總算脫險了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒給「亞人化」的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我暫時只能想到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的確好像沒有亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  連打掃的亞人也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠們去了有更多同類的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信是為了進行融合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若那是真的  我們便能暫時放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算鬆一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是人類  不要嚇我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種地方竟然還有人留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你放心  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.55,0:14:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亞人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我們安定下神來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京已經變成那樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兇殘的亞人  外形古怪的大廈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃去哪裡也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道路四處也封鎖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無處可逃的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時躲到沒有亞人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路上尋找沒有機械的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終來到這個公園
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途中犧牲了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法逃走的人便齊集在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  大概有50人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  在來到這裡前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多人死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表情別那麼沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使只有這麼少人活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也已經要謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  對  全靠我的奮勇表現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是一邊哭一邊逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才對不起  把你們認錯是亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊  我們才好像嚇到你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時候穿成那樣子走出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣都會嚇到人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…這些咖啡和其他食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們從哪裡得來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們輪流去借回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去借
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我們是那樣形容的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡算借啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然要我做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是個警察啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近已經被亞人化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒空發牢騷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這裡有危險  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒騙你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是這一帶才有得賣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地域限定食品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口  那次全靠我吧  蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也喝吧  你的酒量很好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  還有很多  你盡情喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  你們今後有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.83,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要來個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京昨晚在一夜之間面目全非
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不能再去借糧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…跟著  那個課長性騷擾我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙真壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你有聽我講嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  我有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的樣子真古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒量不好便不要喝這麼多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的技術很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.02,0:22:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些究竟…是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇最喜歡的就是研究機械
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.03,0:24:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米奇生性純真  好像玻璃般脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.54,0:24:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對…年紀比我小的男孩沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.57,0:24:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…米奇…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.51,0:24:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我會救你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.71,0:24:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  吹波糖危機

